snippet.title: Sunday Brunch With Akshay Kumar & Tiger Shroff X Kamiya Jani | EP 130 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
On this episode of Sunday Brunch we have the dynamic duo of Bollywood ‚Äì Akshay Kumar and Tiger Shroff! 

Akshay Kumar takes us on a culinary journey, sharing his favorite food joints in Delhi, Mumbai, and Chembur. He spills the beans on his guilty pleasures and offers insights into maintaining a healthy diet. 

He got us some healthy yet delicious food from food vanity that travels with him anywhere he goes. 

Meanwhile, Tiger shares the story behind his name and discusses his love for martial arts and staying fit.
Discover the camaraderie between these two stars as they talk about their journey, both on and off-screen, and their experience working together.

But the fun doesn't end there! Watch as we put their friendship to the test with entertaining games, guaranteed to keep you laughing throughout.

From tasty dishes to laughter-filled moments, this episode is packed with entertainment and offers a glimpse into the special bond shared by "Bade Miya" and "Chote Miya." Share your thoughts in the comments below and join us for an unforgettable Sunday Brunch experience with Akshay Kumar and Tiger Shroff!

snippet.title: ‡¥∏‡µÇ‡¥∞‡µç‡¥Ø‡¥ó‡µç‡¥∞‡¥π‡¥£‡¥Ç - ‡¥∏‡¥§‡µç‡¥Ø‡¥µ‡µÅ‡¥Ç ‡¥Æ‡¥ø‡¥•‡µç‡¥Ø‡¥Ø‡µÅ‡¥Ç | Solar Eclipse April 8 2024 | Solar Eclipse Explained Malayalam
snippet.description:
The world is going to witness a total solar eclipse on April 8 2024. Solar eclipses are rare events for humans. One in every ten thousand people can see a total solar eclipse in their lifetime. This video explains the science behind the event of solar eclipse and why solar eclipses are very rare in nature. The inclination of the moon's orbital plane, the occurrence of lunar nodes, and the alignment of the sun, the moon and the earth in a straight line which leads to the moon's shadow on earth which causes the solar eclipse are explained in this video. There are many myths surrounding solar eclipses like you cannot go out or eat food during a solar eclipse. This video explains why the myths surrounding the solar eclipse are false. This video is a must watch before the solar eclipse 2024 on April 8th.
